arStrings.szText: "Have you seen an old woman in an orange scarf?"
I think I know who you mean...she's been living here some years, one of those who barely made it out of Alcarnus, if, um, if memory serves.
A dissipated local priest. Happy to help, but not much use
Name's... Sophie or something. And doesn't come to church very often. Not that I blame her.
